  "text": "Our study extends the work by Paynter and Edwards [CITATION_1] and reports similar findings, using an evidence base that is now much more extensive than that which existed prior to 2008. We identified a total of 18 quantitative studies and 2 qualitative studies, each of which reported results consistent with a positive association between exposure to POS tobacco promotion and smoking.",
